p: In the matter of the application of Sarah McDunoh for a writ of Habeas Corpus } Return
To the Hon R.A. Jones Judge of said Court.

The respondent Wm Murphy for return to the writ of Habeas Corpus served on him in this matter respectfully shohws the Court, that he is Chief of Police and Keeper of the City jail of the City of Seattle; that he is holding and imprisoning the said Sarah McDunnoh by virtue of a commitment issued by H. Soderberg Esq Justice of the Peace in & for Seattle precinct King Co W.T., a true copy of which said commitment is hereto annexed; nevertheless I here produce the body
